{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">'While Sleeping' is a first-person horror game about experiencing sleep paralysis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are sleeping to go to work tomorrow, and you get sleep paralysis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your body is paralyzed and you can't move, and you can't do anything except look around or close your eyes and open them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have to survive until daybreak by experiencing ghosts and creepy phenomena that appear around you while you are sleeping paralyzed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Playtime: Average 15 ~ 30 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Caution: To create a scary atmosphere, some of the details may be exaggerated compared to actual sleep paralysis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Sleep Paralysis</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/Sleep_Paralysis.gif?t=1734016345\" />You can't move your body. You can only open or close your eyes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Creepy Phenomenon</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/Mysterious_Phenomenon.gif?t=1734016345\" />Creepy phenomena continue to appear as time passes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Don't get caught by ghosts</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/React_Ghost.gif?t=1734016345\" />Each ghost that appears has a different way you should act.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Survive until the sun rises</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/Survive